t","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[4266,1420],"id":"58157673-3bde-433a-b648-f9dc581b2fde","name":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#social","cachedResultName":"#social"},"text":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[4590,1420],"id":"5f2f2e7a-ba0b-428d-be49-cf88e50730c3","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Weekly Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — weekly. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Read Content Calendar (Airtable)","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"1e67608c-8e8c-1868-e20f-6a106222f49d","name":"Note: Weekly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Read Content Calendar (Airtable)\n\nairtable — `search` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Due for Publishing? · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"e60a9702-e8ed-ddc4-7de1-b1994b196956","name":"Note: Read Content Calendar (Airtable)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Due for Publishing?\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Post One at a Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"bfd845b8-8961-06d0-e692-09d050e266af","name":"Note: Due for Publishing?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Post One at a Time\n\nLoop controller — releases 1 item(s) per pass. Output 2 (loop) processes the batch, output 1 (done) fires after the last batch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Count Published · ②→ Publish to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"22f9cc37-9840-a388-4d94-e5624d451832","name":"Note: Post One at a Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Publish to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Space Out Posts · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,1000],"id":"35d03f28-eef8-f8ad-82d4-4367b8cb404f","name":"Note: Publish to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Space Out Posts\n\nPauses 30 seconds — spacing calls to respect rate limits.\n\nNext: Mark Row Published","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,1000],"id":"7fccc9fb-a3dd-4f79-05dd-2b7dcced12e0","name":"Note: Space Out Posts"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Mark Row Published\n\nairtable — `upsert` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Post One at a Time · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,1000],"id":"21503f80-72be-cf52-1fdd-2dbf9a16c67c","name":"Note: Mark Row Published"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Count Published\n\nCollapses all items into a single summary item (for counts and run stats).\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"1cdca7f6-ee8e-2f02-99b8-9b6841d38cda","name":"Note: Count Published"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"6230d8c1-bfcb-5798-0b00-4f442ee3426a","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"ba55ebb7-93de-6f64-41aa-954360507bae","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"5fa72c06-4c02-ed0e-0fd8-f65fc1668e22","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Airtable)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"ba1cafdc-7a47-7d47-c3da-cc6af9f4fb04","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Airtable)\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"275ed61f-a4f8-4639-169f-a007b973f001","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Airtable)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"e2f8f596-1c87-2737-b163-adbcbfa76d67","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,1540],"id":"aa2b2ba8-d3b4-f7e4-c588-0ba74c285dd2","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,1540],"id":"5cd3f319-f865-2a0c-6c32-f212c64a0687","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Schedule the content calendar with Airtable and WordPress automatically\n\n**Pattern:** Social Scheduler · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nSchedule the content calendar with Airtable and WordPress automatically. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual scheduling is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Read Content Calendar (Airtable) → Due for Publishing? → Post One at a Time → Count Published → Tag Pipeline Metadata → Stamp Processing Time → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to social scheduler without manual effort\n- Anyone automating scheduling in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Responds in seconds\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Airtable PAT; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"49a54eb7-5c71-be89-931e-b90a06249f30","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"795db0a3-be1f-fa65-aa40-ce07d8fb35a0","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## ⏱ Rate limiting\n\nWork is batched and spaced with Wait so provider quotas aren't tripped. If you hit 429s, lower the batch size or raise the wait — throughput drops, reliability rises.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"fa880fbe-d701-8c02-20c0-0c601250efe0","name":"⏱ Rate limiting"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your scheduling process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-20],"id":"18dc20af-52e6-a205-cb63-ee5eb8647a46","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Weekly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Read Content Calendar (Airtable)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Read Content Calendar (Airtable)":{"main":[[{"node":"Due for Publishing?","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Due for Publishing?":{"main":[[{"node":"Post One at a Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Post One at a Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Count Published","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Publish to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Publish to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Space Out Posts","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Space Out Posts":{"main":[[{"node":"Mark Row Published","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Mark Row Published":{"main":[[{"node":"Post One at a Time","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Count Published":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Airtable)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Airtable)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"2242a405-e364-4c22-86a0-dd3d5e7322ca","id":"FDX07079"}